Description: Northern Drilling Ltd is a Bermuda-based international offshore drilling contractor to the oil and gas industry. The Company is focused on acquiring and operating modern drilling assets. The Company has two drill ships under construction in Korea. West Aquila and West Libra are its drilling units. Both two units are ultra-deep-water capable drill ships and built for demanding drilling operations in water depths up to 12,000 feet.
